14 "§ 108A-147.11. Health advancement reconciliation adjustment component.
15 (a) The health advancement reconciliation adjustment component is a positive or
16 negative dollar amount equal to the actual nonfederal expenditures for the quarter that is two
17 quarters prior to the current quarter minus the sum of the following specified amounts:
