32 Services shall deposit in the Health Advancement Receipts Special Fund an amount of funds
33 equal to the total nonfederal receipts for health advancement calculated under
34 G.S. 108A-147.3(b) for that quarter, minus the State retention component under G.S. 108A-147.8
