36 under G.S. 108A-147.12(b) for that quarter.amount transferred by the Department of Revenue to
37 the State Treasurer for the Health Advancement Receipts Special Fund under G.S. 105-228.5C.
38 (c) Use of Funds. – The Department of Health and Human Services shall use funds in the
39 Health Advancement Receipts Special Fund only for the purposes described in
40 G.S. 108A-147.13."
