43 the design and construction of the improvements, and the Department or the Authority, if
44 delegated by the Department, shall pay the costs of the design and construction to the business
45 or shall reimburse the business for the costs of the design and construction from the funds
46 allocated under this subsection. For purposes of this subsection, neither the Authority nor the
47 business shall be subject to the provisions of Article 3D of Chapter 143 of the General Statutes
48 or Article 8 of Chapter 143 of the General Statutes.
