1 (2) The amount of funding received by each entity identified pursuant to
2 subdivision (1) of this subsection.
3 (3) The services, training, and equipment purchased with grant funds by each
4 entity that received a grant.
5 (4) Recommendations for the implementation of additional effective school
6 safety measures.
7 SECTION 6.4.(m) Appropriation. – There is appropriated from the General Fund to
8 the Center for Safer Schools the sum of thirty-five million dollars ($35,000,000) in nonrecurring
9 funds for each fiscal year of the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium to be used for the Program established
