34 is necessitated by the fact that selection of an eligible project proposing to
35 provision service via end-to-end fiber-optic facilities to each end-user
36 premises would be cost prohibitive. The Office will develop a methodology
37 for calculating this threshold in a manner that maximizes use of the best
38 available technology while ensuring that the program can, at a minimum, meet
39 the prioritization requirements. The Office will post the methodology for
